As they watched small explosions continued to happen as if in some
sort of chain reactions. Small bursts blowing sand and dirt into the
air, one here and another there until finally a much larger one
appeared revealing a large pit that was at least 30 feet across and 30
feet deep. Inside the pit was a sphere about the size of a basketball
and it was floating in midair about halfway down.

There were the bodies of humans laying at the bottom of the pit.

There was a tunnel leading back into one of the walls, and there was
RODIMUS PRIMAL standing there with his weapon out. He was covered in
dirt, but look none the worse for wear.

&quot;What in the name of Primus was that?&quot; He said as he looked around.

